{
  "id": "69b67950b98a8eee09224f80",
  "title": "大王の御笠山の帯びにせる細谷川の音の清けさ",
  "created": 1773566299,
  "updated": 1773566708,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69b67950b98a8eee09224f80",
      "text": "大王の御笠山の帯びにせる細谷川の音の清けさ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773566299,
      "updated": 1773566299
    },
    {
      "id": "69b6795b00000000005c1728",
      "text": "[萬葉集]（[万葉集]）に載っていた美しい和歌",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773566299,
      "updated": 1773566330
    },
    {
      "id": "69b6797a00000000005c172a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773566331,
      "updated": 1773566331
    },
    {
      "id": "69b6797a00000000005c172b",
      "text": "大王之　　　　おほきみの",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773566331,
      "updated": 1773566450
    },
    {
      "id": "69b679e400000000005c1743",
      "text": "御笠山之　　　みかさのやまの",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773566436,
      "updated": 1773566452
    },
    {
      "id": "69b679e600000000005c1748",
      "text": "帶爾為流　　　おびにせる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773566438,
      "updated": 1773566452
    },
    {
      "id": "69b679e800000000005c174c",
      "text": "細谷川之　　　ほそたにがはの",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773566440,
      "updated": 1773566453
    },
    {
      "id": "69b679e900000000005c174f",
      "text": "音乃清也　　　おとのさやけさ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773566441,
      "updated": 1773566454
    },
    {
      "id": "69b679ea00000000005c1750",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773566443,
      "updated": 1773566443
    },
    {
      "id": "69b6798e00000000005c1731",
      "text": "[美しポイント]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773566351,
      "updated": 1773566637
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67aac00000000005c1752",
      "text": "\t音は [57577] になっており、4 文字の漢字が並んでいる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773566637,
      "updated": 1773566638
    },
    {
      "id": "69b6796500000000005c1729",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773566309,
      "updated": 1773566309
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67ab300000000005c1753",
      "text": "残念ポイント",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773566643,
      "updated": 1773566651
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67ae700000000005c1755",
      "text": "\t大王之だけ 3 文字",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773566695,
      "updated": 1773566708
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67abb00000000005c1754",
      "text": "\t漢字の中に万葉仮名が入っているため 4 文字の漢字と言い切れない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773566652,
      "updated": 1773566691
    },
    {
      "id": "69b67a7300000000005c1751",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773566579,
      "updated": 1773566579
    }
  ]
}